import * as React from "react";
import { List, Datagrid, TextField, ReferenceManyField, EditButton, ShowButton, ChipField, SingleFieldList } from 'react-admin';


export const PostList = props =>(

    <List {...props}>
        <Datagrid>
            <TextField source="id"/>
            <ReferenceManyField label="user" reference="users" target="userId" >
               <SingleFieldList>
                <ChipField source="name"/>
                </SingleFieldList> 
            </ReferenceManyField>
            <TextField source="title"/>
            <TextField source="body"/>
            <EditButton/>
            <ShowButton/>
        </Datagrid>
    </List> 
);
